trans-unit.source: An activation event emitted whenever a user is about to start debugging or about to setup debug configurations.

trans-unit.target: Aktiváló esemény, ami akkor fut, ha a megadott típusú hibakeresési munkamenetnek kell elindulnia (és a megfelelő resolveDebugConfiguration metódusokat meg kell hívni).

trans-unit.source: An activation event emitted whenever a debug session with the specific type is about to be launched and a debug protocol tracker might be needed.
